videos.headline: Melrose: Rask's confidence gets a big boost after win in Montreal
videos.description: Barry Melrose breaks down the Bruins' 3-1 win over the Canadiens, in which Tuukka Rask made 32 saves to record his first career regular-season victory against the Habs.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Analysis (Melrose on Rask's confidence boost) 2015/12/09 SC
